                    <p><span style="font-size: 14px;">The listed measurements are approximates only and may vary slightly depending on the cake. Some cakes may shrink slightly during and/or after baking due to the nature of the ingredients, but were made using standardised cake pans relative to its size.</span></p>
                    <p><span style="font-size: 14px;">Cake information can also be found on the individual cake product page.</span></p>
                    <br>
